r908 | deveiant | 2002-10-24 17:22:46 -0700 (Thu, 24 Oct 2002) | 5 lines

- Fixed the longstanding bug in which non-MUES exceptions which occurred in
  worker threads caused the server to crash. Forgot to fully-qualify 'Exception'
  in the rescue clause. Thanks to GhostGanz from
  irc://irc.openprojects.net/#ruby-lang for the fix.

