r724 | deveiant | 2002-10-03 22:14:33 -0700 (Thu, 03 Oct 2002) | 15 lines

- Fixed step indexing to make it harder to put the questionnaire in an
  inconsistant state.

- Fixed bug caused by not calling super() in the initializer.

- Added attribute accessors for @currentStepIndex, @steps, and @name.

- Added a @result ivar that keeps the result of the finalizer callback so a
  questionnaire can be used as a passive collector.

- Added new methods #addSteps, #removeSteps, #undoSteps, #skipSteps.

- Moved progression through the steps into #askNextQuestion so its name is a bit
  closer to its function.

