r587 | deveiant | 2002-07-31 20:13:42 -0700 (Wed, 31 Jul 2002) | 8 lines

:BROKEN:

- Initial work to make command-definition use object instances instead of a raft
  of singletons (Thanks to suggestions made by Alexis Lee
  <red@FaerieMUD.org>). The change is not yet complete, but I wanted to get the
  design committed. This also means there's too many changes to document
  effectively.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r586 | deveiant | 2002-07-31 20:09:43 -0700 (Wed, 31 Jul 2002) | 7 lines

- Modified the socket-related events to deal with the Listener abstraction
  instead. To wit, SocketEvent is now ListenerEvent, from which are derived
  ListenerConnectEvent and ListenerErrorEvent.

- Grafted a parent class for UntrappedSignalEvent, SignalEvent, into the
  heirarchy to handle signals which *have* been trapped.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r585 | deveiant | 2002-07-31 20:06:08 -0700 (Wed, 31 Jul 2002) | 5 lines

- Made an initial stab at ripping out the coupling of CommandShell to User.

- Renamed the lastLogin attribute 'lastLoginDate' to clarify what sort of value
  it contains.

