r581 | deveiant | 2002-07-31 20:00:35 -0700 (Wed, 31 Jul 2002) | 13 lines

- Converted to use FactoryMethods to allow derivatives to be easily create and
  used.

- Stripped leading underscores from method names.

- Changed the way the visitor is specified/used/created, as it is really the
  role of the Environment to decide how it gets to the objectstore in question.

- Split retrieve into a two-phase operation to facilitate de-coupling of MM and
  backend.

- Added requires of base extension classes.

