------------------------------------------------------------------------
r495 | deveiant | 2002-06-06 07:22:23 -0700 (Thu, 06 Jun 2002) | 18 lines

- Module: Changed implements? to use Module#include? rather than Module#<.

- MUES::Debuggable: Split debugMsg off into a module function rather than an
  instance method.

- MUES::Debuggable: Re-added #_debugMsg alias for backward-compatibility.

- MUES::Object: Changed funky #__GenerateMuesId() protected instance method into
  a class method: MUES::Object::generateMuesId( obj )

- MUES::Object: Renamed #finalizer to #makeFinalizer to be more indicative of
  what it's actually doing.

- MUES::Object: Moved 'objectStoreData' attribute into MUES::StorableObject, as
  the ObjectStore shouldn't need to store anything in a non-storable object.

- MUES::Object: Relocated #lull and #awaken to MUES::StorableObject.

