r268 | red | 2001-12-06 05:38:26 -0800 (Thu, 06 Dec 2001) | 9 lines

Some indentation commits. Sorry.

Little bit of error checking in Namespace.rb (search on 'Red'). I'm issuing
debugmsg at level 1 if validTypes or requiredMethods contains any nil
elements- please change the level if appropriate.

Catches a little bug in DummyAdapter which set a player's dbinfo to nil after
the SavePlayerInfo (or whatever) event was handled.

