------------------------------------------------------------------------
r126 | deveiant | 2001-07-17 19:23:03 -0700 (Tue, 17 Jul 2001) | 15 lines

- Lots of major changes:

  - Fleshed out the shell so commands are singleton instances of classes derived
    from an associated class, MUES::CommandShell::Command, instead of hardcoded
    in a case statement.

  - Increased decoupling of shell class from the classes it interacts with.  A
    context object now provides an interface to objects with which the shell may
    require interaction.

  - Moved all user-modifiable shell attributes (eg., the prompt string) to a
    hash which is modifiable with the 'set' command.

  - Added approximate command-string matching, and a built-in help mechanism

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r125 | deveiant | 2001-07-17 19:09:01 -0700 (Tue, 17 Jul 2001) | 2 lines

- Removed dependency on deprecated 'Debugging.rb'

