r51 | deveiant | 2001-04-08 01:23:53 -0700 (Sun, 08 Apr 2001) | 2 lines

Initial release.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r50 | deveiant | 2001-04-08 01:23:08 -0700 (Sun, 08 Apr 2001) | 21 lines

- Renamed the class to TableAdapter

- Moved header to README.rd.en in toplevel directory

- Made the ObjectCache and RowState inner classes threadsafe

- Renamed RowState#replace() to RowState#setState()

- Improved method/general comments

- Made TableAdapter.lookup() accept an optional block for iteration

- Publicized most of the class methods

- Removed code that set default values for row state in
  TableAdapter#initialize()

- Added TableAdapter#delete() method.

- Split out the accessor and the writer for TableAdapter#rowid()

------------------------------------------------------------------------
