r42 | deveiant | 2001-04-06 01:19:20 -0700 (Fri, 06 Apr 2001) | 7 lines

- Added initial code necessary to support prioritized (and Comparable) events

- Added LoginSessionEvent, LoginSessionFailureEvent, LoginSessionAuthEvent, and
  CallbackEvent to support the new LoginSession authentication mechanism.

- Removed PlayerLoginFailureEvent and PlayerAuthenticationEvent classes

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r41 | deveiant | 2001-04-06 01:19:20 -0700 (Fri, 06 Apr 2001) | 2 lines

- Added player and allow/deny table fetching/storing functions

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r40 | deveiant | 2001-04-06 01:19:20 -0700 (Fri, 06 Apr 2001) | 3 lines

- Added an instance attribute (objectStoreData) to the MUES::Object class to
  support storage of ObjectStore metadata.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r39 | deveiant | 2001-04-06 01:19:20 -0700 (Fri, 06 Apr 2001) | 5 lines

- Removed unnecessary restriction in addFilters() and removeFilters() which
  required the stream to be in the RUNNING state.

- Touched up array-handling to avoid unnecessary flatten!()s

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r38 | deveiant | 2001-04-06 01:19:20 -0700 (Fri, 06 Apr 2001) | 6 lines

