------------------------------------------------------------------------
r18 | deveiant | 2001-03-28 14:23:05 -0800 (Wed, 28 Mar 2001) | 25 lines

- Modified require to reflect name change of the Namespace module

- Reorganized and added some documentation in the header, and cleaned up the
  rest of the docs

- Added Jeremiah to the Author section

- Simplified state constants since they're in their own namespace

- Replaced the authenticatePlayer() method with an event handler,
  _handlePlayerAuthenticationEvent()

- Changed _eventLoop() method to _mainThreadRoutine() to better reflect what it
  does.

- Made initialize() a protected method

- Changed the 'database' config key to 'objectstore'

- Removed the thread code from the main listener socket's accept() loop, as it
  was old crufty experimental code to try to track down errors on the client
  sockets.

- Modified the IOEventStream code to reflect changes in those classes

------------------------------------------------------------------------
