r8 | deveiant | 2001-03-19 23:54:08 -0800 (Mon, 19 Mar 2001) | 5 lines

- Changed the ENV directory name to avoid potential clashes with other adapters.

- Changed the {store,fetch}Object() methods to pluralized ones to reflect
  changes in the ObjectStore class.

