r7 | deveiant | 2001-03-19 23:40:46 -0800 (Mon, 19 Mar 2001) | 2 lines

- Added a inner AdapterError class

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6 | deveiant | 2001-03-19 23:40:07 -0800 (Mon, 19 Mar 2001) | 7 lines

- Fixed bug in fetchObjects() caused by missing final statement in collect()

- Moved lull() outside of storage collect() loop in storeObjects() so objects
  are lulled *before* they're stored. Duh. *selfbonk*

- Documented callback block in comments for {store,fetch}Objects()

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r5 | deveiant | 2001-03-19 23:34:47 -0800 (Mon, 19 Mar 2001) | 5 lines

- Modified methodology so including Debuggable is less intrusive. It now adds
  singleton attributes to objects instead of depending on a global class
  attribute added via a class_eval() in the append_features() hook. This makes
  it possible to do per-object debugging as well as per-class debugging.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
